<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Follow-Up to a postponed issue ZF-2802.</p>

<p>Zend_Loader cannot handle php 5.3 namespaces, it just replaces underscores to directories but should also do this with namespace separator.</p>

<p>Afaik this is also what the PHP Standards Group already discussed and Doctrine2 is already using it this way.</p>

